    Enumeration of available component names / functionalities. These are the standard types of components. Other types of components may be added to an agent (TODO).

    The enumeration entries also contain information about the default implementation of the specified component type. The name of the implementation class can be given when creating the entry, or can be inferred based on the name of the entry and the constants in the enumeration.
